*msmtp-1.1.2-r1 (08 Jul 2004)

  08 Jul 2004; Tom Martin <slarti@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.1.2-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bumped for gsasl support, through virtual/gsasl. Temporarily removed
  ~ppc and ~x86 till someone can test this.

*msmtp-1.1.2 (01 Jul 2004)

  01 Jul 2004; Grant Goodyear <g2boojum@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.0.0.ebuild,
  +msmtp-1.1.2.ebuild:
  Version bump (closes bug # 53054)

  22 Jun 2004; Danny van Dyk <kugelfang@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.0.0.ebuild:
  Marked ~amd64.

  03 Jun 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> msmtp-1.0.0.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

*msmtp-1.0.0 (31 May 2004)

  31 May 2004; Grant Goodyear <g2boojum@gentoo.org> +msmtp-1.0.0.ebuild:
  New package.  Thanks to Martin Lambers (bug # 33423) and 
  Tom Martin (Bug # 49400)!

